{
  "style": "IEEE",
  "texts": [
    "Specifically, we use different LLMs for navigational sequential landmark extraction, including ChatGPT (used by our CONSOLE), GPT-3 [17] (the predecessor of ChatGPT), Vicuna [58] (a recent strong open source alternative to ChatGPT which has two sizes--7B and 13B), and Spacy [59] (a NLP library), and feed the extracted landmarks into the consequent modules.",
    "We access the APIs of ChatGPT and Vicuna [58] in May, 2023.",
    "We access the API of GPT-3 [17] in Dec, 2022.",
    "The results are given in Table 8.",
    "From Table 8 we can observe that: 1) ChatGPT outperforms other competitors in most metrics; 2) GPT-3, Vicuna13B, and Vicuna7B are comparable to Chat-GPT in some metrics; 3) Vicuna13B outperforms Vicuna7B especially in SPL; 4) Spacy performs the worst among all competitors."
  ],
